Be going to 

We can use be going to make predictions about the future based on the situation now. 

It's cloudy. (situation now) -> It's going to rain. (prediction)

It's sunny. (situation now) -> It's not going to rain. (prediction)

Is it going to rain?
Yes, it is. / No, it isn't.

What's going to happen?
He's going to be fired.
